    ese puñado de historias nace CABROCHICO.
  </p>

  <article class="grid w-full grid-cols-2 gap-4">
    <img src="/img/revenga cover.png" />
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">REVENGA! // LAST ALBUM</h2>

      <a href="">
        <img
          src="/img/spotify-logo.svg"
          class="inline-block h-[30px] mt-[3px]"
        />
      </a>
      <a href="">
        <img
          src="/img/apple-music-logo.svg"
          class="inline-block h-[23px] ml-[10px]"
        />
      </a>

      <RoundButton>LISTEN NOW</RoundButton>
    </div>
  </article>

